Enum AreaOfInterest.AoiDisplay

  • java.lang.Object

    public static enum AreaOfInterest.AoiDisplay
extends java.lang.Enum<AreaOfInterest.AoiDisplay>
    Represents the ways that the area of interest (aoi) can be rendered on the map.

    • Enum Constant Summary

      Enum Constants 
      Enum Constant and Description
      CLIP
      Set a clip for the area (IE only show the area of interest).
      NONE
      Do not show the Area of interest on the map.
      RENDER
      Draw the entire map and render the AOI polygon on the map.

    • Enum Constant Detail

      • RENDER

        public static final AreaOfInterest.AoiDisplay RENDER
        Draw the entire map and render the AOI polygon on the map. This is the default.

      • CLIP

        public static final AreaOfInterest.AoiDisplay CLIP
        Set a clip for the area (IE only show the area of interest).

      • NONE

        public static final AreaOfInterest.AoiDisplay NONE
        Do not show the Area of interest on the map. In this case another processor will likely make use of the AOI.
